Package: ivctools
Title: IV-Compass Diagnostics for Single-Instrument Exogeneity
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Naram", "Gwak", email = "naram.gwak@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for the IV-Compass (IVC) diagnostic, which assesses the
    exogeneity of a single instrument in pretest-posttest designs by comparing
    a conventional instrumental-variable estimate with a compass-corrected
    benchmark derived from the pretest. Provides estimation, an analytic
    method-of-moments and bootstrap inference for the diagnostic contrast,
    simulation-based power analysis, and visualization.
